6月12日，本季首场热带风暴在[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]最西侧成型<ref name="metadata">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | author3 = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141109063506/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/metadata_1936.html | deadurl = no | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT) Meta Data, 1936 | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's Office of Oceanic & Atmospheric Research | date = 2012-12 | accessdate = 2017-01-04 | archivedate = 2014-11-09 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/metadata_1936.html }}</ref><ref name="hurdat">{{cite web | author = Atlantic hurricane research division | year = 2009 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/tracks1851to2009_atl_reanal.txt | title = Atlantic hurricane database (HURDAT) "best track" (1851–2008) | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administrations | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2011-01-02 | accessdate = 2011-01-02 | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110102071538/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/tracks1851to2009_atl_reanal.txt }}</ref>。当天下午，墨西哥近海多艘船只遭遇狂风大浪，墨西哥气象局驻[[切图马尔|切图马尔]]办事处率先发布报告宣布[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]形成<ref name="MWR">{{cite web | author = Jean Galleen | title = North Atlantic Tropical Disturbances of 1939 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303195500/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1939.pdf | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1939.pdf | publisher = Weather Bureau | year = 1939 | accessdate = 2017-01-04 | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] }}</ref>。风暴向西移动，路线同[[伯利兹|伯利兹]]海岸平行，然后进入[[尤卡坦半岛|尤卡坦半岛]]东北角上空。气旋继续稳步北上经过[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]并缓慢增强，于6月14日达到[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]每小时80公里、最低气压1000[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，29.53[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度<ref name="hurdat" /><ref name="MWR" />。受北侧的[[高气压|高气压区]]影响，风暴行进路线形成逆时针环路，但又因[[低压槽|低压槽]]影响转向北上，于6月16日以热带风暴下限强度从[[阿拉巴马州|阿拉巴马州]][[莫比尔_(阿拉巴马州)|莫比尔]]附近登陆。转向西北后，气旋迅速减弱成热带低气压，最终于6月17日在[[密西西比州|密西西比州]]上空消散。<ref name="hurdat" />

佛罗里达州西部和阿拉巴马州在风暴来袭前收到[[热带气旋警告|风暴警告]]，建议低洼地区居民转移到地势更高的地点<ref>{{cite news | title = Gale Winds Expected Along Florida Coast | date = 1939-06-15 | newspaper = The Daily Capital News}}</ref>。气旋造成的破坏程度很轻，仅导致一名男童跌入暴涨的河中溺毙<ref name="MWR" />。
